itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description: In today's episode, you get to meet Jensen, he's finally here!! We'll be talking about Brooklin's pregnancy, labor, delivery, postpartum, and Jenna's birth experiences from 20 years ago and how things have changed! We also discussed and answered many of your questions regarding natural birth, tearing, epidurals, etc.
